node.text: A year ago today I surprised my mom flying back to Chicago on her Birthday in what would be the last time I ended up seeing her. She would be 65 today. Not a day goes by where I don’t think about her and reflect. I miss you mom. I miss our daily facetimes, our jokes, our secrets, your morning texts, heath links you’d send, your recipes, you ALWAYS checking in to make sure I’m ok and safe. I miss the void of not just your unconditional love & support always, but also my best friend. I miss you, I love you, I appreciate you, & today I honor you & your life. Always on my mind, forever in my heart. Happy Birthday, love mamas boy.❤️

node.text: Kale chips are one of our go to treats to dehydrate, as you can see maybe Noah a little more obsessed than me😜. This simple dog friendly ranch recipe consist of soaked cashews, water, nooch and a little dill. We used A @tribestlife Sedona Supreme dehydrator. It has 9 stainless steel mesh trays, 1 BPA-Free Closed tray to collect debris, TST (Two-Stage Sequential Temperature-Timer) Feature for Faster Safer Dehydration, all-digital controls & display, continuous operation mode, a powerful central fan and a pretty cool internal LED light. Does it get any better? It’s also super quiet compared to other dehydrators I’ve used in the past. For those who aren’t aware, dehydrating takes out the moisture but doesn’t kill enzymes or have nutrient degradation due. I’ve always said a juicer, blender and dehydrator are keys to making eating this way super smooth and easy! If you’re in the market for a dehydrator, definitely check these out!

node.text: Health doesn’t come from an injection, procedure or pill. Health is found when we align w/the laws of nature. We’ve become so disconnected w/ it that it truly doesn’t surprise me we’re in the situation we’re in. Thrown in schools young, stripped of our creative potential & forced to sit in a chair & memorize an indoctrination to groom you into the matrix for the corporate & tech conglomerates & very few that control every aspect of our lives. You won’t find ANY food that has a speck of nutrition in those school systems to help think straight, just sugar loaded & overly processed cooked garbage. From then we enter the matrix in debt from college loans & are sold the dream. Find a corporate job, become a doctor(another indoctrination by r@ckafeller/ph@rma)make money, get that car & sign off on a mortgage. Now you’re off! In a cubicle or office space you go, 8-10 hours a day. Our morning Starbucks, the only nature or movement we see is our walk from our car to the office, then home plop on our couches & watch & fed more lies, fear & fast food commercials on TV. Then we order or microwave food, most of the time its processed & unhealthy. We become dependent on energy stimulants from not getting energy from our food being overfed & undernourished, become overweight & disbiotic chasing the carrot on the stick. Then we go to doctors who prescribe you a drug for your symptom. Sound familiar? I’VE LIVED IT. We’ve been sold a lie. YOUR HEALTH is your number 1 priority. Without it we have NOTHING. GET ALIGNED WITH NATURE! Everything thrives! Trees/plants blossoming & you don’t see obese animals because they’re eating & living the way they’re designed to. Health is when our mental, emotional & physical bodies are aligned. How do we start? Well you have FREE medicine in sunlight, fresh air, breath work, meditation, prayer & movement. From there EAT REAL FOOD, to keep a healthy gut, strong immune system & strong intuition so you can see through the bullshit lies we’ve been & are currently being sold. Then we can peel back the layers of conditioning & step back into our true nature, power & sovereignty. I love you, GOD BLESS YOU.❤️

node.text: September 12th will be one year I lost my mom tragically. Anyone who can relate & has experienced something traumatic like this can attest there’s no limit or timeline to grieve. I stopped everything. I stopped eating raw & juicing daily, stopped moving, stopped posting, stopped caring. I fell into a dark place, contemplating life & even moving forward. When people asked how I’m doing it was “I’m ok” but I wasn’t. People I love in my immediate circle saw my struggle. They continued to worry yet be there everyday to lift me but again, the process can’t be forced. I was eating cooked food that turned to processed vegan products, put on weight, had zero drive & lost motivation. As low as I was I never turned to alcohol or pharma drugs like Prozac, Zoloft, etc because I know those doctor prescribed drugs would put me in a worse state than I was already in. Looking back I’m grateful for my 8 year health awakening & faith because had this been when I was sick, drinking & on pharma drugs, I wouldve self destructed & not turned it around. I didn’t suppress my emotions. I walked thru fire, opened my heart to all feels, emotions & cries. Then, things starting turning. For one, my faith in Christ reignited from so many happenings & experiences you just can’t make up. I started going back to the gym & started incorporating juices again. The process was slow & seemed to level a bit. That was until I REALLY disciplined myself, took self responsibility & started a 90 day protocol consisting of 96 oz of juice, raw & 42 supplements a day. I never was a supp guy but today being day 46 here in Hawaii, this protocol has LITERALLY given me & brought me back to LIFE. It’s unfortunate western medicine look down upon this form of healing when in reality NO PHARMACEUTICAL DRUG HEALS ANYTHING. I’ve done 6 colonics where I’ve moved STUFF you wouldn’t imagine especially after being raw almost 6 years. Everything in the protocol is what nature provides including the high quality supps (puradyme). I don’t make a penny off them, but they have integrity. So my answer how to heal from anything? It’s simple, forgiveness, have an OPEN HEART, NATURE & YOUR CREATOR. I love you, God bless you.❤️

Just plug the machine in, switch on, add seeds, and in 5 to 8 days you’ll be enjoying your fresh organically-grown sprouts, without the use of soil, chemicals, or special lighting. Bring the excitement of indoor organic gardening into your home all year round. The Freshlife 3000 Automatic Sprouter is an easy way to provide you, your pup or family with fresh, living sprouts and nutritious baby vegetables grown in your own kitchen garden NO SOIL NEEDED😱. If you’re also not sure where to pick up sprouts, I’ll be using and highly recommend my people the @sproutman sprouts which are also 100% organic! Check them out for the amazing variety and selection. 
.
.
Why should you sprout? Sprouts are a highly nutritious, IMMUNE SUPPORTING food and you definitely get all your bang for your buck, plus they’re super easy to grow.
